data.description: Welcome Home!! This charming and cozy home nestled on a corner lot in the vibrant city of San Antonio, Texas is ready to be called home!    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The well-designed layout seamlessly connects the spacious living area into the kitchen and dining area creating an ideal flow for both everyday living, and entertaining guests.    In the heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The ample counter space is perfect for preparing delicious meals, and creating lasting memories with family and friends.   Add a roll in butcher block countertop and you're ready to entertain!     The adjacent dining area offers a cozy spot for enjoying meals together.  Featuring five bedrooms, there is plenty of space for everyone in the family or the flexibility to create a home office, gym, or hobby room. The two bathrooms are thoughtfully designed, providing convenience and comfort for the entire household.    Additional highlight of this property is its prime corner lot location, providing additional outdoor space, and enhancing curb appeal. The backyard offers a private retreat, ideal for outdoor gatherings, BBQ's, playtime, or just relaxing under the Texas sky.   This home enjoys proximity to a variety of amenities, including SAISD schools, parks, HEB, shopping centers, and dining options. The neighborhood exudes a sense of community, making it an ideal place to call home.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 715 Pebblebrook Dr. your new home sweet home in San Antonio. Schedule a showing today and discover the charm and comfort this property has to offer! Closing cost assistance, or rate buy down help is available!
